Tool Tracking Project

About:

This project is a surgical tool tracking system which detects and
localises minimally invasive video in video images. The system
incorporates a Random Forest classifier and a level-set based
segmentation system to determine pose in 3D dimenesions.

Dependencies:

OpenCV v2.3.1 or higher
TooN

Install Guide:

Linux - Grab the makefile from the build directory and copy to the
root directory. Build as usual.   

Windows - Copy the VS2010 solution to the root directory and build.

OS-X - Code does not support OS-X

